Title: Sitemap-Include
Tags: headers, sitemap, sitemap-headers
+-Tags: *

<p>
    The <b>Sitemap-Include</b> header controls whether a node is eligible for
    inclusion in the <a href="{{node-url:generated}}">generated sitemap</a>.
</p>

<p>There are two possible values:</p>

<ul>
    <li><i><a href="{{node-url:headers/sitemap-include/true}}">true</a></i></li>
    <li><i><a href="{{node-url:headers/sitemap-include/false}}">false</a></i></li>
</ul>

<p>The default value is <i>true</i>.</p>

